00:43:50.798 --> 00:43:52.800
Are you okay?

532
00:43:53.568 --> 00:43:54.802
Is Carter?

533
00:43:54.869 --> 00:43:56.637
Yeah. we're both fine.

534
00:43:56.704 --> 00:43:58.806
Please don't lie to me.

535
